android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_ME.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground with the type "mediaPlayback".

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_MI.info: permits foreground services with microphone use.
android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE_MI.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground with the type "microphone".

com.android.vending.BILLING.description: Allows an application to make in-app purchases from Google Play.

com.google.android.finsky.permission.BIN.description: A custom permission defined by Google.

com.google.android.gms.permission.AD_ID.description: This app uses a Google advertising ID and can possibly serve advertisements.

android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_ATT.info: allow applications to access advertising service attribution
android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_ATT.description: This enables the app to retrieve information related to advertising attribution, which can be used for targeted advertising purposes. App can gather data about how users interact with ads, such as clicks or impressions, to measure the effectiveness of advertising campaigns.

android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_AD_.info: allow app to access the device's advertising ID.
android.permission.ACCESS_ADSERVICES_AD_.description: This ID is a unique, user-resettable identifier provided by Google's advertising services, allowing apps to track user behavior for advertising purposes while maintaining user privacy.

metadata.cwe: CWE-330: Use of Insufficiently Random Values
metadata.description: The App uses an insecure Random Number Generator.
App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.

metadata.cwe: CWE-532: Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File
metadata.description: The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.

metadata.cwe: CWE-89: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')
metadata.description: App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.
This App uses SSL certificate pinning to detect or  prevent MITM attacks in secure communication channel.

metadata.cwe: CWE-312: Cleartext Storage of Sensitive Information
metadata.description: Files may contain hardcoded sensitive information like usernames, passwords, keys etc.
This App may have root detection capabilities.

metadata.cwe: CWE-749: Exposed Dangerous Method or Function
metadata.description: Insecure WebView Implementation. Execution of user controlled code in WebView is a critical Security Hole.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327: Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: SHA-1 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327: Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: MD5 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.
App can write to App Directory. Sensitive Information should be encrypted.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327: Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: The App uses ECB mode in Cryptographic encryption algorithm. ECB mode is known to be weak as it results in the same ciphertext for identical blocks of plaintext.
App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327: Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: Calling Cipher.getInstance("AES") will return AES ECB mode by default. ECB mode is known to be weak as it results in the same ciphertext for identical blocks of plaintext.

"LastNightAboutWokeUp" : "Réveil est l'heure à laquelle vous vous réveillez et désactivez le suivi. Essayez de maintenir une heure de réveil régulière. Un manque de régularité au réveil peut perturber votre rythme circadien et augmenter le risque de développer des troubles sévères du sommeil. Une perturbation des rythmes circadiens peut bouleverser la régularité du sommeil et vous empêcher de vous endormir au bon moment, ce qui entraînera un manque de sommeil. "sleepNoteTagDescription_Environment_ColdRoom" : "La température corporelle et la température de la chambre affectent également considérablement la qualité du sommeil. L'été ou dans des endroits chauds, la chaleur extrême peut vous empêcher de passer une bonne nuit de sommeil. D'après une étude, la température de la pièce a un impact plus important sur la qualité de sommeil que le bruit environnant. D'après d'autres études, lorsque la température de la pièce ou du corps est élevée, la qualité du sommeil diminue et la vigilance augmente. Une température d'environ 20°C semble être la plus confortable pour la plupart des gens, bien qu'elle dépende des préférences et des habitudes."

"sleepNoteTagDescription_PreSleep_Milk" : "Drinking a glass of warm milk before bed is an old tradition that has been passed down through generations as a way of relaxation, relieving anxiety, and having a comfortable sleep. Most experts agree that milk's potential for improving sleep may be related to the specific chemical components or psychological influences with soothing sleep habits - or perhaps a combination of both. One theory suggests that certain compounds in milk - specifically tryptophan and melatonin - can help you fall asleep. Another theory says that drinking hot milk subconsciously reminds you of the past how you had a glass of milk before bedtime when you were a toddler. These soothing feelings may remind your brain that it's time to sleep, making it easier for you to fall asleep calmly."

In this way, there is no certain and one-size-fits-all length of sleep, what is important is to be able to find the best length of sleep for you so that you wake up and feel rested, with a sound mind and refreshed body. "sleepNoteTagDescription_PreSleep_Milk" : "Ein Glas warme Milch vor dem Schlafengehen zu trinken, ist eine alte Tradition, die über Generationen hinweg als Mittel zur Entspannung, zum Abbau von Ängsten und für einen angenehmen Schlaf weitergegeben wurde. Die meisten Experten sind sich einig, dass die schlaffördernde Wirkung der Milch mit den spezifischen chemischen Bestandteilen oder psychologischen Einflüssen auf die Schlafgewohnheiten zusammenhängt - oder vielleicht mit einer Kombination aus beidem. Eine Theorie besagt, dass bestimmte Verbindungen in der Milch - insbesondere Tryptophan und Melatonin - beim Einschlafen helfen können. Eine andere Theorie besagt, dass das Trinken von heißer Milch Sie unbewusst an die Zeit erinnert, als Sie als Kleinkind vor dem Schlafengehen ein Glas Milch tranken. Diese beruhigenden Gefühle können Ihr Gehirn daran erinnern, dass es Zeit zum Schlafen ist, so dass es Ihnen leichter fällt, ruhig einzuschlafen."

Uma teoria sugere que certos compostos do leite - em particular o triptofano e a melatonia, podem ajudar a adormecer. Outra teoria diz que beber leite quente remete subconscientemente para o passado, quando, em bebé, bebia leite quente antes de ir dormir. playstore_details.title: ShutEye®: Sleep Tracker
playstore_details.description:
Embark on a journey into the realm of serene slumber and tranquility, guided by the captivating melodies of ShutEye's innovative sleep sounds. Welcome to the world of ShutEye: the ultimate sleep-tracking app that empowers you to take control of your sleep like never before.

Elevate Your Sleep Quality:
ShutEye is tailored to enhance your sleep quality. Amid its array of functionalities, the brilliance of the sleep sounds feature stands out, offering an auditory escape into dreamscapes crafted to whisk you away from daily stresses and guide you into restful slumber.

Unveil Sleep Patterns:
Uncover the mysteries of your sleep patterns and decode the intricate nuances influencing your sleep cycle with our state-of-the-art sleep-tracking technology. Our innovative sleep recorder enables you to capture moments of nighttime whispers and laughter, allowing you to share these cherished memories with loved ones.

Wake Refreshed:
Arise from slumber revitalized and invigorated with the groundbreaking alarm feature. Moreover, the snore detector keeps you informed about your sleep quality, ensuring you're always in the know about your nighttime habits.

Universally Embracing:
ShutEye is designed to be inclusive, catering to a diverse range of individuals seeking improved sleep quality. Craft your personalized symphony of white noise and nature's melodies to create a sleep environment that aligns perfectly with your preferences.

Seize Better Sleep:
The significance of quality sleep cannot be overstated. Don't let sleep troubles hinder your overall well-being. Seize the opportunity today to download the ShutEye sleep tracker and embark on your journey towards profound, rejuvenating rest, harmonized by the soothing embrace of sleep sounds.

Embrace Sweet Dreams:
With the promise of sweet dreams and a brighter tomorrow, it's time to embrace a new chapter of restful sleep. Allow the symphony of ShutEye's sleep sounds to guide you into tranquil slumber and experience the transformation firsthand.

Welcome to a world where your sleep takes center stage. Welcome to ShutEye.

ShutEye is registered trademark of Enerjoy. (Reg. No.6463393)
